title: 2016 KNVB Cup Final
text: The 2016 KNVB Cup Final was a <a href="Association%20football">football</a> match between <a href="Feyenoord">Feyenoord</a> and <a href="FC%20Utrecht">FC Utrecht</a> on 24 April 2016 at <a href="De%20Kuip">De Kuip</a>, <a href="Rotterdam">Rotterdam</a>. It was the final match of the <a href="2015%E2%80%9316%20KNVB%20Cup">2015–16 KNVB Cup</a> competition and the 98th Dutch Cup Final. Feyenoord beat Utrecht 2–1 to win their first domestic cup since 2008 and their 12th in total.
